217
00:16:21,689 --> 00:16:23,399
Especially you, Mun.

218
00:16:55,806 --> 00:16:59,643
<i>What you're seeing right now</i>
<i>is the barrier.</i>

219
00:17:00,477 --> 00:17:04,231
<i>Someone from Yung</i>
<i>or someone who's with them</i>

220
00:17:04,314 --> 00:17:06,400
