<i>once they're trapped in this barrier,</i>

223
00:17:13,824 --> 00:17:16,285
<i>and they can't use any powers</i>
<i>like psychokinesis.</i>

224
00:17:17,661 --> 00:17:21,415
<i>On the other hand,</i>
<i>Counters will lose their spiritual powers</i>

225
00:17:21,498 --> 00:17:22,958
