229
00:17:35,012 --> 00:17:36,138
<i>But remember,</i>

230
00:17:37,139 --> 00:17:39,933
<i>in order to use your power</i>
<i>within this barrier,</i>

231
00:17:40,601 --> 00:17:41,977
<i>you need Yung's territory.</i>

232
00:17:43,062 --> 00:17:47,316
<i>That means, Mun, you must be</i>
<i>in full control of the territory.</i>

233
00:17:47,983 --> 00:17:49,526
