as well as the ones inside.

243
00:18:34,655 --> 00:18:37,282
Everyone, remember.

244
00:18:38,450 --> 00:18:40,077
When the territory is gone,

245
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:41,995
the barrier will be gone too.

246
00:18:42,079 --> 00:18:43,914
