<i>the territory to me</i>

259
00:19:38,051 --> 00:19:39,219
<i>at will.</i>

260
00:19:40,220 --> 00:19:42,848
<i>This isn't good enough.</i>
<i>We won't stand a chance.</i>

261
00:20:23,347 --> 00:20:24,223
